title: Time Team - Season 08 (2001) - 12 Episodes
description:
Time Team - Season 08 (2001) - 13 Episodes

Season Summary:
Time Team's eighth season has the team digging up a Norman castle, a leper hospital in Hampshire and looking for an iron-age village on Salisbury Plain - in the middle of a tank-training zone!

S08E01 - The Anglo-Saxon Cemetery in Lincolnshire - Normanton, Lincolnshire
S08E02 - The Man Who Bought a Castle - Alderton, Northamptonshire
S08E03 - The Celtic Spring - Llygadwy, Wales
S08E04 - A Waltham Villa - Waltham Field, Whittington, Gloucestershire
S08E05 - The Lost Viaduct - Blaenafon, South Wales
S08E06 - A Palace Sold for Scrap - Rycote, Oxfordshire
S08E07 - An Iron-Age Roundhouse - Salisbury Plain, Hampshire
S08E08 - The Inter-City Villa - Basildon, Berkshire
S08E09 - Holy Island - Lindisfarne, Northumberland
S08E10 - The Leaning Tower of Bridgnorth, Shropshire
S08E11 - Three Tales of Canterbury - Canterbury, Kent
S08E12 - The Leper Hospital - Winchester, Hampshire
